block.comment: Smaller speeds it up, bigger slows it down

scripts.comment: Welcome to the Tower of Hanoi recursion homework! Your job is to fill in the body of the "Hanoi move ..." block below.

block-definition.s: Hanoi move %'pieces' pieces from %'from' to %'to' with spare %'spare'

scripts.comment: Fill in the body. All you need to do is call yourself and the "move top piece from _ to _" block below, obviously with some control structures in your base case to know when to stop recursing. Enjoy!

block.l: How many disks for your Tower of Hanoi game (1-7)?
